# âœ¨ Truth Be Told  (PROTOTYPE AT BOTTOM)
### Reimagining the Volunteer Experience with Empathy and Clarity

> A civic UX case study focused on improving the onboarding experience for volunteers supporting incarcerated women.

---

## ğŸ” Overview

**Truth Be Told** is a nonprofit dedicated to empowering incarcerated women through storytelling, connection, and community. Their volunteer program is a vital part of that mission â€” but the digital experience left volunteers feeling uncertain, disconnected, and unsupported.

Our UX team reimagined the volunteer journey from the ground up: making it clearer, warmer, and more empowering for first-time and returning volunteers alike.

