**UX Researcher / Civic Designer**

- Conducted volunteer interviews and synthesized pain points
- Created a detailed persona and journey map
- Helped define design opportunities rooted in emotional clarity
- Co-designed wireframes and prototypes using Figma
- Facilitated testing sessions with new volunteer candidates

